# Copy to .env and fill in. Bun auto-loads .env; .env is gitignored.
# Throwaway GameForge/Metin2 accounts only.
#
# Credentials are NOT read from here — `auth login` takes --email/--password or prompts,
# deliberately, so a stray value in .env can't hijack a login.

# 1 writes the account store as readable JSON — debugging only, never on a real store.
UNFORGE_STORE_PLAINTEXT=
